if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('tbl_product_supp_rel') and o.name = 'FK_TBL_PROD_REFERENCE_BUSI_PRO')
alter table tbl_product_supp_rel
drop constraint FK_TBL_PROD_REFERENCE_BUSI_PRO
go

alter table tbl_product_supp_rel
add constraint FK_TBL_PROD_REFERENCE_BUSI_PRO foreign key (ProID)
references busi_product (ProID)
go
